---
source: tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Lint term consistency in project docs

Usage: mf term lint [OPTIONS] [PATH]

Arguments:
  [PATH]  

Options:
      --fix
          Auto-fix issues that have a fixer
      --root <PATH>
          Mind Repo root directory
      --config <PATH>
          Config file path
      --rule <RULE>
          Restrict to a specific lint rule kind
      --severity <LEVEL>
          Only emit issues at or above this severity (error|warning|info)
  -v, --verbose...
          Verbose output
      --max-warnings <N>
          Exit 1 when warnings exceed this count
  -q, --quiet
          Silence non-error output
      --dry-run
          Preview fixes without writing (only with --fix)
      --format <FORMAT>
          Output format [default: text] [possible values: text, json]
      --all
          Apply all corrections including suggested
      --json
          Shorthand for --format json
      --no-color
          Disable colored output
  -y, --yes
          Skip the interactive confirmation prompt (required in non-TTY)
  -f, --force
          Alias for --yes
  -p, --project <NAME>
          Project name for project-scoped operations
      --install-completion <INSTALL_COMPLETION>
          Install shell completion script [possible values: bash, zsh, fish, powershell, elvish]
      --show-completion <SHOW_COMPLETION>
          Show shell completion script [possible values: bash, zsh, fish, powershell, elvish]
  -h, --help
          Print help
  -V, --version
          Print version
